Three separate artillery attacks struck a hospital in Northern Sri Lanka
killing nine people and injuring many more. _Ramblings of A Mind_
[condemns](http://ramblingsmind.blogspot.com/2009/02/condemn-attacks-on-
hospital.html) the attacks on the hospital. _Chitrangi_
[discusses](http://chitrangi.wordpress.com/2009/02/02/who-said-the-truth-icrc-
or-army-spokesman/) who could be behind this.

